# Define custom check missing values (columns on)
def check_missing_columns(df):
    index = 0
    for col in df:
        missing_count = df[col].isna().sum()
        if missing_count > 0:
            index += 1
            print(f"{col}: {missing_count}")
    print(f"\nTotal Missing Columns: {index}")
